Package: SimSurvey
Type: Package
Title: A tool for the simulation testing of the design and analysis of
    fisheries-independent trawl surveys
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
            "Paul Regular <Paul.Regular@dfo-mpo.gc.ca> [aut, cre]",
            "Jonathan Babyn <Jonathan.Babyn@dfo-mpo.gc.ca> [ctb]",
            "Greg Robertson <Greg.Robertson@dfo-mpo.gc.ca> [ctb]"
          ))
Maintainer: Paul Regular <Paul.Regular@dfo-mpo.gc.ca>
Description: This package simulates stratified-random samples from 
    a spatially-correlated age-structured population to provide a tool for the 
    simulation testing of the design and analyses of fisheries-independent trawl
    surveys.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
